      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute dream of a car, and it is in truly stunning condition! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been kept sparkling clean and runs like a dream. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to find a new home with someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
