    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system, both meticulously serviced for optimal valve timing and throttle response. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. This vehicle exhibits no fluid seepage, zero bushing deflection, and a pristine undercarriage, representing a collector-grade specimen with peak mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
